descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i750.photobucket.com/albums/xx141/ninjakamihana/Diverse/Lorena%20barx.jpg[/img]

My preset for an elegant and slightly gothic looking Ningheim character I named Lorena.
She was inspired by 80's goth/punk, but I wanted to make the requirements as few as possible.
I vary her look with warpaint, piercings and tattoos, so feel free to go wild!
She looks great as a vampire hunter or a sorceress!

Required:
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474/?]The Ningheim Race
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty [/url] + the Ningheim addon you will find on the comments page for the Ningheim Race

That should be it! I use the 4K UNP body.
author: Kamihana
